### Key Components

#### Database Schema
- **Users**: Extended with an `enum` column (`role`) defaulting to `employee`.
- **Tasks**: Contains `title`, `description`, `due_date`, `status`, and `assigned_user_id`.

#### Filament Admin Widgets
The [StatsOverviewWidget](file:///c:/Users/hassa/OneDrive/Desktop/TaskMaster/app/Filament/Widgets/StatsOverviewWidget.php#10-41) displays metrics dynamically scoped to current conditions (`Total Open`, `Completed This Week`, [Overdue](file:///c:/Users/hassa/OneDrive/Desktop/TaskMaster/app/Models/Task.php#30-36)). The [OverdueTasksWidget](file:///c:/Users/hassa/OneDrive/Desktop/TaskMaster/app/Filament/Widgets/OverdueTasksWidget.php#11-52) lists tasks pending past their due date. 

#### Livewire Task List Component
The employee dashboard relies on [app/Livewire/TaskList.php](file:///c:/Users/hassa/OneDrive/Desktop/TaskMaster/app/Livewire/TaskList.php), which queries only tasks assigned to the currently authenticated user. Status buttons instantly dispatch an update and visually re-sort the grid without full-page reloads.

